# Local dev data the training-era modules used to generate.  v1.3.0
# stopped shipping / training any local model, so these patterns are
# kept only as a safety net in case an old workflow drops a binary
# into the repo; the canonical contents of models/ is a single
# .gitkeep and data/ is now just a dev cache.
data/*.edf
data/*.csv

